a k\u7923  c\u7887  l\u7841 , tr\'e2n c\u7847 m d\u7883  th\'fa, ng\u7885 c ng\'e0 v\'e0ng b\u7841 c... c\'e1c th\u7913  \u273 \'e1 qu\'fd, c\'e1c c\'e2y tr\u7847 m, \u273 \'e0n c\'f9ng c\'e1c s\u417 n h\'e0o h\u7843 i v\u7853 t kh\'f4ng thi\u7871 u th\u7913  g\'ec, kh\'ed h\u7853 u b\u7889 n m\'f9a kh\'f4ng l\u7841 nh kh\'f4ng n\'f3ng, \u272 \u7871  Lai r\u7845 t \'e1i m\u7897 , vui qu\'ean tr\u7903  v\u7873 . D\'e2n ph\u432 \u417 ng Nam kh\u7893  v\'ec b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i B\u7855 c ph\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c y\'ean s\u7889 ng nh\u432  x\u432 a m\u7899 i c\'f9ng g\u7885 i Long Qu\'e2n r\u7857 ng: "B\u7889  \u417 i \u7903  \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 \u273 \u7875  cho d\'e2n B\u7855 c x\'e2m nhi\u7877 u ph\u432 \u417 ng d\'e2n".\
Long Qu\'e2n \uc0\u273 \u7897 t nhi\'ean tr\u7903  v\u7873 , th\u7845 y\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%82u_C%C6%A1"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \'c2u C\uc0\u417 }}\'a0c\'f3 dung m\uc0\u7841 o \u273 \u7865 p \u273 \u7869  k\u7923  l\u7841 , trong l\'f2ng vui m\u7915 ng, b\'e8n h\'f3a th\'e0nh m\u7897 t trang thi\u7871 u ni\'ean phong t\u432  t\'fa l\u7879 , t\u7843  h\u7919 u k\u7867  h\u7847 u ng\u432 \u7901 i h\u7841  \u273 \'f4ng \u273 \'fac, v\u7915 a \u273 i v\u7915 a ca h\'e1t \u273 \'e1nh tr\u7889 ng. Cung \u273 i\u7879 n t\u7921  nhi\'ean d\u7921 ng l\'ean. \'c2u C\u417  vui l\'f2ng theo Long Qu\'e2n. Long Qu\'e2n gi\u7845 u \'c2u C\u417  \u7903  Long \u272 \'e0i. Nham \u272 \u7871  Lai tr\u7903  v\u7873 , kh\'f4ng th\u7845 y \'c2u C\u417 , sai qu\u7847 n th\u7847 n \u273 i t\'ecm kh\u7855 p thi\'ean h\u7841 . Long Qu\'e2n c\'f3 ph\'e9p th\u7847 n th\'f4ng bi\u7871 n h\'f3a th\'e0nh tr\u259 m h\'ecnh v\u7841 n tr\u7841 ng y\'eau tinh, qu\u7927  s\u7913 ,\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "%22https"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 r\uc0\u7891 ng}},\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/R%E1%BA%AFn"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 r\uc0\u7855 n}},\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/H%E1%BB%95"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 h\uc0\u7893 }},\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Voi"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 voi}}... l\'e0m cho b\uc0\u7885 n \u273 i t\'ecm \u273 \u7873 u s\u7907  h\'e3i kh\'f4ng d\'e1m s\u7909 c s\u7841 o, \u272 \u7871  Lai b\'e8n ph\u7843 i tr\u7903  v\u7873 . Truy\u7873 n ng\'f4i \u273 \u7871 n \u273 \u7901 i Du V\'f5ng, th\'ec\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Xi_V%C6%B0u"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 Xuy V\uc0\u432 u}}\'a0l\'e0m lo\uc0\u7841 n. Vua n\u432 \u7899 c H\u7919 u H\'f9ng l\'e0\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ho%C3%A0ng_%C4%90%E1%BA%BF"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 Hi\'ean Vi\'ean}}\'a0\uc0\u273 em ch\u432  h\u7847 u t\u7899 i \u273 \'e1nh nh\u432 ng kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c. Xuy V\u432 u m\'ecnh th\'fa m\'e0 n\'f3i ti\u7871 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i, c\'f3 s\u7913 c kh\u7887 e d\u361 ng m\'e3nh. C\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i d\u7841 y Hi\'ean Vi\'ean d\'f9ng tr\u7889 ng da th\'fa l\'e0m l\u7879 nh, Xuy V\u432 u s\u7907  h\'e3i ch\u7841 y v\u7873  \u273 \u7845 t Tr\'e1c L\u7897 c. \u272 \u7871  Du V\'f5ng x\'e2m l\u259 ng ch\u432  h\u7847 u, c\'f9ng\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ho%C3%A0ng_%C4%90%E1%BA%BF"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 Hi\'ean Vi\'ean}}\'a0giao binh \uc0\u7903  Ph\u7843 n Tuy\u7873 n \u273 \'e1nh ba tr\u7853 n \u273 \u7873 u b\u7883  thua, b\u7883  gi\'e1ng phong \u7903  \u273 \u7845 t l\u7841 c \u7845 p r\u7891 i ch\u7871 t \u7903  \u273 \'f3. Gi\'f2ng h\u7885 \'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipe"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 Th\uc0\u7847 n N\'f4ng}}\'a0t\uc0\u7899 i \u273 \'e2y th\'ec h\u7871 t. Long Qu\'e2n l\u7845 y\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%82u_C%C6%A1"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \'c2u C\uc0\u417 }}\'a0r\uc0\u7891 i \u273 \u7867  ra m\u7897 t b\u7885 c, cho l\'e0 \u273 i\u7873 m b\u7845 t th\u432 \u7901 ng, v\u7913 t ra c\'e1nh \u273 \u7891 ng; qua s\'e1u b\u7843 y ng\'e0y, b\u7885 c v\u7905  ra m\u7897 t tr\u259 m qu\u7843  tr\u7913 ng, m\u7895 i tr\u7913 ng n\u7903  ra m\u7897 t con trai, m\u7899 i \u273 em v\u7873  nh\'e0 nu\'f4i. Kh\'f4ng ph\u7843 i b\'fa m\u7899 m, c\'e1c con t\u7921  l\u7899 n l\'ean, tr\'f4ng \u273 \u7865 p \u273 \u7869  k\u7923  d\u7883 , ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'e0o c\u361 ng tr\'ed d\u361 ng song to\'e0n, ng\u432 \u7901 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7873 u k\'ednh tr\u7885 ng cho l\'e0 tri\u7879 u phi th\u432 \u7901 ng. Long Qu\'e2n \u7903  l\'e2u d\u432 \u7899 i Th\u7911 y qu\u7889 c v\u7907  con th\u432 \u7901 ng mu\u7889 n v\u7873  \u273 \u7845 t B\u7855 c.\
V\uc0\u7873  t\u7899 i bi\'ean gi\u7899 i,\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ho%C3%A0ng_%C4%90%E1%BA%BF"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 Ho\'e0ng \uc0\u272 \u7871 }}\'a0nghe n\'f3i r\uc0\u7845 t s\u7907  h\'e3i cho binh ra gi\u7919  c\u7917 a \u7843 i, m\u7865  con\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%82u_C%C6%A1"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \'c2u C\uc0\u417 }}\'a0kh\'f4ng th\uc0\u7875  v\u7873  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c b\'e8n quay v\u7873  n\u432 \u7899 c Nam m\'e0 g\u7885 i Long Qu\'e2n r\u7857 ng: "B\u7889  \u7903  n\u417 i n\'e0o m\'e0 \u273 \u7875  m\u7865  con t\'f4i c\'f4 \u273 \u7897 c, ng\'e0y \u273 \'eam bu\u7891 n kh\u7893  th\u7871  n\'e0y". Long Qu\'e2n b\u7895 ng tr\u7903  v\u7873 , g\u7863 p nhau \u7903  \u273 \u7845 t T\u432 \u417 ng. \'c2u C\u417  n\'f3i: "Thi\u7871 p v\u7889 n l\'e0 ng\u432 \u7901 i n\u432 \u7899 c B\u7855 c, \u7903  v\u7899 i vua, sinh h\u7841  \u273 \u432 \u7907 c tr\u259 m con trai, vua b\u7887  thi\u7871 p m\'e0 \u273 i, kh\'f4ng c\'f9ng thi\u7871 p nu\'f4i con, l\'e0m ng\u432 \u7901 i v\'f4 phu v\'f4 ph\u7909 , ch\u7881  bi\u7871 t th\u432 \u417 ng m\'ecnh". Long Qu\'e2n n\'f3i: "Ta l\'e0 n\'f2i\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/R%E1%BB%93ng"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 r\uc0\u7891 ng}}, \uc0\u273 \u7913 ng \u273 \u7847 u th\u7911 y t\u7897 c, n\'e0ng l\'e0 gi\u7889 ng\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ti%C3%AAn"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 ti\'ean}}, s\uc0\u7889 ng \u7903  tr\'ean \u273 \u7845 t, tuy kh\'ed \'e2m d\u432 \u417 ng h\u7907 p l\u7841 i m\'e0 sinh ra con, nh\u432 ng th\u7911 y h\u7887 a t\u432 \u417 ng kh\u7855 c, gi\'f2ng gi\u7889 ng b\u7845 t \u273 \u7891 ng, kh\'f3 \u7903  l\'e2u v\u7899 i nhau \u273 \u432 \u7907 c, nay ph\u7843 i chia ra. Ta \u273 em n\u259 m m\u432 \u417 i con v\u7873  Th\u7911 y ph\u7911  chia tr\u7883  c\'e1c x\u7913 , n\u259 m m\u432 \u417 i con theo n\'e0ng v\u7873  \u7903  tr\'ean \u273 \u7845 t, chia n\u432 \u7899 c m\'e0 tr\u7883 . L\'ean n\'fai, xu\u7889 ng b\u7875 , h\u7919 u s\u7921  b\'e1o cho nhau bi\u7871 t, \u273 \u7915 ng qu\'ean".\
