\f1\b0 \cf2 L\uc0\u7841 c \u272 \'e0 v\u7889 n l\'e0 chim th\u7847 n s\u7889 ng tr\'ean tr\u7901 i, s\u7843 i c\'e1nh c\u7911 a \'f4ng \u273 \u7911  che l\u7845 p to\'e0n b\u7897  m\u7863 t \u273 \u7845 t, m\u7895 i l\u7847 n \'f4ng \u273 \u7853 p c\'e1nh l\'e0 gi\'f4ng b\'e3o l\u7841 i n\u7893 i l\'ean. M\u7897 t l\u7847 n \'f4ng \u273 \u7871 n th\u259 m L\u7897 c T\u7909 c v\'e0 t\u7863 ng qu\'e0 cho nh\u7919 ng \u273 \u7913 a con trai c\u7911 a L\u7897 c T\u7909 c. \'c2u Long Qu\'e2n l\'e0 con trai c\u7843  n\'ean nh\u7853 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c qu\u7843  tr\u7913 ng ti\'ean, \u7903  b\'ean trong ch\'ednh l\'e0 con c\u7911 a L\u7841 c \u272 \'e0. Chim th\u7847 n kh\'f4ng qu\'ean d\u7863 n r\u7857 ng khi qu\u7843  tr\u7913 ng n\u7903  ra th\'ec ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean m\'e0 con g\'e1i \'f4ng nh\'ecn th\u7845 y s\u7869  ch\'ednh l\'e0 ch\u7891 ng c\u7911 a c\'f4. Sau \u273 \'f3 L\u7841 c \u272 \'e0 chia tay m\u7885 i ng\u432 \u7901 i ra v\u7873 , n\'e0o ng\u7901  \u273 \'fang l\'fac \u273 \'f3 \u273 \u7913 a con trai \'fat S\'f9ng L\'e3m c\u7911 a L\u7897 c T\u7909 c ra \u273 \u7901 i, v\'ec ch\u7881  chu\u7849 n b\u7883  t\'e1m m\'f3n qu\'e0 n\'ean L\u7841 c \u272 \'e0 kh\'f4ng c\'f2n c\'e1ch n\'e0o kh\'e1c b\'e8n l\u7845 y t\'ean c\u7911 a m\'ecnh \u273 \u7863 t cho S\'f9ng L\'e3m. K\u7875  t\u7915  \u273 \'f3 v\u7873  sau \u273 \u7913 a con \'fat c\u7911 a L\u7897 c T\u7909 c \u273 \u432 \u7907 c g\u7885 i l\'e0 L\u7841 c Long Qu\'e2n.\
L\uc0\u7897 c T\u7909 c m\u7845 t \u273 i khi\u7871 n \u273 \u7845 t n\u432 \u7899 c\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/X%C3%ADch_Qu%E1%BB%B7"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 X\'edch Qu\uc0\u7927 }}\'a0b\uc0\u7883  chia c\u7855 t, chi\u7871 n tranh lo\u7841 n l\u7841 c li\'ean mi\'ean nh\u432 ng \'c2u Long Qu\'e2n v\u7851 n kh\'f4ng qu\'ean l\u7901 i d\u7863 n c\u7911 a L\u7841 c \u272 \'e0, \'f4ng lu\'f4n mang theo qu\u7843  tr\u7913 ng b\'ean m\'ecnh m\u7885 i l\'fac m\u7885 i n\u417 i kh\'f4ng bao gi\u7901  r\u7901 i xa d\'f9 ch\u7881  n\u7917 a b\u432 \u7899 c v\'e0 \u273 \u7863 t t\'ean n\'f3 l\'e0\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%82u_C%C6"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \'c2u C\uc0\u417 }}. \uc0\u272 \u7875  \'fd th\u7845 y v\'f9ng \u273 \u7845 t\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/L%E1%BA%A1c_Vi%E1%BB%87t"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 L\uc0\u7841 c Vi\u7879 t}}\'a0ph\'eda nam v\uc0\u7855 ng ch\u7911  n\'ean \'c2u Long Qu\'e2n li\u7873 n k\'e9o qu\'e2n \u273 \u7871 n x\'e2m chi\u7871 m. D\'e2n ph\u432 \u417 ng Nam kh\u7893  v\'ec b\u7883  ng\u432 \u7901 i B\u7855 c ph\u432 \u417 ng qu\u7845 y nhi\u7877 u, kh\'f4ng \u273 \u432 \u7907 c y\'ean s\u7889 ng nh\u432  x\u432 a m\u7899 i c\'f9ng g\u7885 i Long Qu\'e2n r\u7857 ng: "B\u7889  \u417 i \u7903  \u273 \'e2u m\'e0 \u273 \u7875  cho d\'e2n B\u7855 c x\'e2m nhi\u7877 u ph\u432 \u417 ng d\'e2n". L\u7841 c Long Qu\'e2n li\u7873 n quay v\u7873  c\u7913 u gi\'fap ng\u432 \u7901 i d\'e2n. \'c2u Long Qu\'e2n b\u7883  L\u7841 c Long Qu\'e2n \u273 \'e1nh b\u7841 i, ng\u7901  \u273 \'e2u tr\'ean \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng th\'e1o ch\u7841 y th\'ec qu\u7843  tr\u7913 ng l\u7841 i r\u417 i xu\u7889 ng \u273 \u7845 t v\u7905  n\'e1t, \u273 \u7875  l\u7897  b\'ean trong l\'e0 m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i con g\'e1i t\'ed hon. V\'e0 r\u7891 i ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\'f4 g\'e1i th\u7845 y ch\'ednh l\'e0 L\u7841 c Long Qu\'e2n. \'c2u Long Qu\'e2n \u273 au l\'f2ng v\'ec b\u7841 i tr\u7853 n v\'e0 m\u7845 t \u273 i ng\u432 \u7901 i m\'ecnh y\'eau qu\'fd n\'ean m\u7845 t s\u7899 m, v\'f9ng \u273 \u7845 t\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%82u_Vi%E1%BB%87t"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \'c2u Vi\uc0\u7879 t}}\'a0c\uc0\u361 ng r\u417 i v\'e0o h\u7895 n lo\u7841 n. \'c2u C\u417  qu\u7843  nhi\'ean c\'e0ng l\u7899 n c\'e0ng xinh \u273 \u7865 p, n\'e0ng c\'f3 l\'f2ng t\u7915  bi v\'e0 c\'f3 t\'e0i v\u7873  y thu\u7853 t th\u432 \u7901 ng xuy\'ean theo L\u7841 c Long Qu\'e2n \u273 i t\u7913  ph\u432 \u417 ng ch\u7919 a b\u7879 nh gi\'fap ng\u432 \u7901 i. Sau \u273 \'f3 L\u7841 c Long Qu\'e2n v\'e0\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%82u_C%C6%A1"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \'c2u C\uc0\u417 }}\'a0l\uc0\u7845 y nhau sinh ra m\u7897 t b\u7885 c tr\u259 m tr\u7913 ng n\u7903  ra m\u7897 t tr\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i con. M\u7897 t h\'f4m L\u7841 c Long Qu\'e2n b\u7843 o \'c2u C\u417 :\'a0
\f4\i "Ta l\'e0 gi\uc0\u7889 ng\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/R%E1%BB%93ng"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 R\uc0\u7891 ng}}, m\'ecnh l\'e0 gi\uc0\u7889 ng\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ti%C3%AAn"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 Ti\'ean}},\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Th%E1%BB%A7y_(Ng%C5%A9_h%C3%A0nh)"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 th\uc0\u7911 y}}\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/H%E1%BB%8Fa_(Ng%C5%A9_h%C3%A0nh)"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 h\uc0\u7887 a}}\'a0kh\uc0\u7855 c nhau, kh\'f4ng \u7903  c\'f9ng nhau \u273 \u432 \u7907 c". Hai ng\u432 \u7901 i b\'e8n chia con m\'e0 \u7903  ri\'eang.
