Sau khi chia tay v\uc0\u7899 i Qu\u7889 c m\u7851 u\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%82u_C%C6%A1"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \'c2u C\uc0\u417 }}, L\uc0\u7841 c Long Qu\'e2n c\'f9ng 50 ng\u432 \u7901 i con c\'f2n l\u7841 i xu\'f4i \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng l\u7847 n ra\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bi%E1%BB%83n_%C4%90%C3%B4ng"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 Nam H\uc0\u7843 i}}. \uc0\u272 \u7871 n \u273 \u7845 t\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/B%C3%ACnh_%C4%90%C3%A0"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 B\'ecnh \uc0\u272 \'e0}}\'a0b\'e2y gi\uc0\u7901  (x\'e3\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/B%C3%ACnh_Minh,_Thanh_Oai"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 B\'ecnh Minh}}, huy\uc0\u7879 n\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thanh_Oai"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 Thanh Oai}}, th\'e0nh ph\uc0\u7889 \'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/H%C3%A0_N%E1%BB%99i"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 H\'e0 N\uc0\u7897 i}}, c\'e1ch bi\uc0\u7875 n kh\'f4ng xa, s\'f4ng n\u432 \u7899 c m\'eanh mang, L\u7841 c Long Qu\'e2n truy\u7873 n cho c\'e1c con d\u7915 ng ch\'e2n d\u7921 ng tr\u7841 i, n\u7893 i l\u7917 a n\u7845 u \u259 n. \u272 i d\u7841 o kh\u7855 p v\'f9ng m\u7897 t l\u432 \u7907 t, th\u7845 y th\u7871  \u273 \u7845 t n\u417 i \u273 \'e2y m\'e0u m\u7905 , s\'f4ng su\u7889 i l\u432 \u7907 n quanh, nhi\u7873 u th\u7873 m \u273 \u7845 t cao mang d\'e1ng long ch\u7847 u h\u7893  ph\u7909 c, b\'e8n quy\u7871 t \u273 \u7883 nh ch\u7885 n \u273 \u7845 t n\'e0y l\'e0m n\u417 i d\u7921 ng x\'e2y c\u417  nghi\u7879 p. Ng\'e0y ng\'e0y, L\u7841 c Long Qu\'e2n c\'f9ng qu\u7847 n th\u7847 n v\u259 n v\'f5 d\u7841 y d\'e2n tr\u7891 ng d\'e2u nu\'f4i t\u7857 m d\u7879 t v\u7843 i, \u273 u\u7893 i di\u7879 t th\'fa d\u7919 . L\u7841 i truy\u7873 n cho c\'e1c con l\u7921 a ch\u7885 n d\'e2n ch\'fang kh\u7887 e m\u7841 nh, t\u7887 a \u273 i kh\u7855 p v\'f9ng duy\'ean h\u7843 i khai kh\u7849 n \u273 \u7845 t hoang, l\u7845 n bi\u7875 n m\u7903  mang b\u7901  c\'f5i... Ch\u7859 ng bao l\'e2u, c\u7843  v\'f9ng \u273 \u7845 t v\u7899 i trung t\'e2m l\'e0 B\u7843 o C\u7921 u cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng d\'e2n l\'e0nh \u273 \'e3 tr\u7903  n\'ean tr\'f9 ph\'fa, m\u7885 i th\u7843 o kh\u7845 u trong v\'f9ng b\u7883  d\u7865 p tan. Ru\u7897 ng \u273 \u7891 ng, l\'e0ng x\'f3m ng\'e0y m\u7897 t m\u7903  r\u7897 ng, h\'ecnh th\'e0nh n\'ean nh\u7919 ng l\'e0ng x\'f3m \u273 \u7847 u ti\'ean c\u7911 a\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ch%C3%A2u_th%E1%BB%95_s%C3%B4ng_H%E1%BB%93ng"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 ch\'e2u th\uc0\u7893  s\'f4ng H\u7891 ng}}\'a0sau n\'e0y. L\'fac \uc0\u7845 y, d\'e2n s\u7889 ng \u7903  ven bi\u7875 n, xu\u7889 ng n\u432 \u7899 c \u273 \'e1nh c\'e1 th\u432 \u7901 ng b\u7883  gi\u7889 ng\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thu%E1%BB%93ng_lu%E1%BB%93ng"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 giao long}}\'a0l\'e0m h\uc0\u7841 i, b\'e8n n\'f3i v\u7899 i vua. \u272 \'e1p: "Gi\u7889 ng s\u417 n man v\'e0 gi\u7889 ng th\u7911 y t\u7897 c c\'f3 th\'f9 v\u7899 i nhau, th\u432 \u7901 ng gh\'e9t nhau cho n\'ean h\u7841 i nhau \u273 \'f3". Khi\u7871 n ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \u7901 i l\u7845 y m\u7921 c x\u259 m v\'e0o m\'ecnh theo h\'ecnh Long Qu\'e2n, theo d\u7841 ng th\u7911 y qu\'e1i. T\u7915  \u273 \'f3, d\'e2n kh\'f4ng b\u7883  tai h\u7885 a giao long l\'e0m h\u7841 i n\u7919 a. T\u7909 c x\u259 m m\'ecnh c\u7911 a d\'e2n\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/B%C3%A1ch_Vi%E1%BB%87t"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 B\'e1ch Vi\uc0\u7879 t}}\'a0c\uc0\u361 ng b\u7855 t \u273 \u7847 u t\u7915  \u273 \u7845 y.\
H\uc0\u7891 i qu\u7889 c s\u417 , d\'e2n kh\'f4ng \u273 \u7911  \u273 \u7891  d\'f9ng, ph\u7843 i l\u7845 y v\u7887  c\'e2y l\'e0m \'e1o, d\u7879 t c\u7887  gianh l\'e0m chi\u7871 u, l\u7845 y c\u7889 t g\u7841 o l\'e0m r\u432 \u7907 u, l\u7845 y c\'e2y quang lang, c\'e2y tung l\u432  l\'e0m c\u417 m (c\'f3 ch\u7895  vi\u7871 t l\'e0 u\u7889 ng), l\u7845 y c\u7847 m th\'fa, c\'e1, ba ba l\'e0m m\u7855 m, l\u7845 y r\u7877  g\u7915 ng l\'e0m mu\u7889 i, c\u7845 y b\u7857 ng dao, tr\u7891 ng b\u7857 ng l\u7917 a. \u272 \u7845 t s\u7843 n xu\u7845 t \u273 \u432 \u7907 c nhi\u7873 u g\u7841 o n\u7871 p, l\u7845 y \u7889 ng tre m\'e0 th\u7893 i c\u417 m. B\u7855 c g\u7895  l\'e0m nh\'e0 \u273 \u7875  tr\'e1nh h\u7893  s\'f3i. C\u7855 t t\'f3c ng\u7855 n \u273 \u7875  d\u7877  \u273 i l\u7841 i trong r\u7915 ng r\'fa. \u272 \u7867  con ra l\u7845 y l\'e1 chu\u7889 i l\'f3t cho n\u7857 m, c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i ch\u7871 t th\'ec gi\'e3 c\u7889 i l\'e0m l\u7879 nh, ng\u432 \u7901 i l\'e2n c\u7853 n nghe ti\u7871 ng \u273 \u7871 n c\u7913 u. Ch\u432 a c\'f3\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 tr\uc0\u7847 u cau}}, vi\uc0\u7879 c h\'f4n th\'fa gi\u7919 a nam n\u7919  l\u7845 y g\'f3i \u273 \u7845 t l\'e0m \u273 \u7847 u, sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7899 i gi\u7871 t tr\'e2u d\'ea l\'e0m \u273 \u7891  l\u7877 , l\u7845 y c\u417 m n\u7871 p \u273 \u7875  nh\u7853 p ph\'f2ng c\'f9ng \u259 n, sau \u273 \'f3 m\u7899 i th\'e0nh th\'e2n. \u272 \'f3 tr\u259 m ng\u432 \u7901 i con trai ch\'ednh l\'e0 t\u7893  ti\'ean c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipe"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 B\'e1ch Vi\uc0\u7879 t}}\'a0v\uc0\u7853 y.\
V\'e0o m\uc0\u7897 t ng\'e0y cu\u7889 i\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Th%C3%A1ng_Hai"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 th\'e1ng Hai}}\'a0l\uc0\u7883 ch tr\u259 ng, tr\u7901 i b\u7895 ng nhi\'ean n\u7893 i d\'f4ng gi\'f3, s\u7845 m ch\u7899 p l\'f3e s\'e1ng c\u7843  v\'f9ng, Qu\u7889 c t\u7893  \u259 n v\u7853 n trang ph\u7909 c oai phong, l\u7851 m li\u7879 t, th\'e2n th\u432 \u417 ng nh\'ecn c\'e1c con ch\'e1u v\'e0 d\'e2n l\'e0ng m\u7897 t l\u432 \u7907 t r\u7891 i h\'f3a trong \u273 \'eam. C\u7843 m th\u432 \u417 ng v\'e0 t\u7887  l\'f2ng tri \'e2n v\u7899 i ng\u432 \u7901 i c\'f3 c\'f4ng khai h\'f3a v\'f9ng \u273 \u7845 t B\u7843 o C\u7921 u n\'e0y, vua quan c\'f9ng d\'e2n l\'e0ng t\u7893  ch\u7913 c l\u7877  tang linh \u273 \'ecnh, t\'e1ng ng\'e0i t\u7841 i g\'f2 \u273 \u7845 t cao nh\u7845 t v\'f9ng, l\u7853 p mi\u7871 u (nay l\'e0\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C4%90%E1%BB%81n_N%E1%BB%99i_B%C3%ACnh_%C4%90%C3%A0"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \uc0\u272 \u7873 n N\u7897 i B\'ecnh \u272 \'e0}}) quanh n\uc0\u259 m th\u7901  ph\u7909 ng. C\u7893  l\'f4i ng\u7885 c ph\u7843  hi\u7879 n l\u432 u gi\u7919 \'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C4%90%E1%BB%81n_H%C3%B9ng"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \uc0\u272 \u7873 n H\'f9ng}}\'a0(ni\'ean hi\uc0\u7879 u Th\'e1i B\'ecnh th\u7913  hai-{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/971"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 971}}) c\'f3 ghi "M\uc0\u7897  (L\u7841 c Long Qu\'e2n) t\'e1ng t\u7841 i Ba \u272 \u7889 ng (Ba G\'f2) \u273 \u7891 ng th\u432 \u7907 ng B\u7843 o C\u7921 u, h\u7853 u c\u7843 i B\u7843 o \u272 \'e0".\
