\f1\b0 \cf2 \uc0\u7902 \'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bi%E1%BB%83"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 bi\uc0\u7875 n \u272 \'f4ng}}\'a0c\'f3 con tinh ng\uc0\u432  x\'e0 (c\'f2n g\u7885 i l\'e0 Ng\u432  Tinh) d\'e0i h\u417 n n\u259 m m\u432 \u417 i tr\u432 \u7907 ng, ch\'e2n nhi\u7873 u nh\u432  ch\'e2n r\u7871 t, bi\u7871 n h\'f3a v\u7841 n tr\u7841 ng, linh d\u7883  kh\'f4n l\u432 \u7901 ng, khi \u273 i th\'ec \u7847 m \u7847 m nh\u432  m\u432 a, l\u7841 i \u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c th\u7883 t ng\u432 \u7901 i n\'ean ai c\u361 ng s\u7907 .\
Thu\uc0\u7903  \u7845 y c\'f3 h\'f2n \u273 \'e1 Ng\u432  Tinh, r\u259 ng \u273 \'e1 l\u7903 m ch\u7903 m c\u7855 t ngang b\u7901  b\u7875 , \u7903  d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \'e1 c\'f3 hang, Ng\u432  Tinh s\u7889 ng \u7903  trong \u273 \'f3. V\'ec s\'f3ng gi\'f3 hi\u7875 m tr\u7903 , kh\'f4ng c\'f3 l\u7889 i th\'f4ng, d\'e2n mu\u7889 n m\u7903  m\u7897 t \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i kh\'e1c nh\u432 ng \u273 \'e1 r\u7855 n kh\'f3 \u273 \u7869 o. Thuy\u7873 n c\u7911 a nh\'e2n d\'e2n \u273 i qua ch\u7895  n\'e0y th\u432 \u7901 ng hay b\u7883  Ng\u432  Tinh l\'e0m h\u7841 i. \u272 \'eam kia c\'f3 b\u7885 n ng\u432 \u7901 i ti\'ean \u273 \u7909 c \u273 \'e1 l\'e0m \u273 \u432 \u7901 ng \u273 i \u273 \u7875  cho h\'e0nh nh\'e2n c\'f3 ch\u7895  qua l\u7841 i. Ng\u432  Tinh b\'e8n h\'f3a l\'e0m con g\'e0 tr\u7855 ng g\'e1y \u7903  tr\'ean n\'fai. Qu\u7847 n ti\'ean nghe ti\u7871 ng ng\u7905  r\u7857 ng \u273 \'e3 r\u7841 ng \u273 \'f4ng b\'e8n c\'f9ng bay l\'ean tr\u7901 i.\
L\uc0\u7841 c Long Qu\'e2n th\u432 \u417 ng d\'e2n b\u7883  h\u7841 i b\'e8n h\'f3a ph\'e9p th\'e0nh m\u7897 t chi\u7871 c thuy\u7873 n c\u7911 a th\u432 \u7901 ng d\'e2n, h\u7841  l\u7879 nh cho\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/D%E1%BA%A1-xoa"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 qu\uc0\u7927  D\u7841  Thoa}}\'a0\uc0\u7903  Th\u7911 y ph\u7911  c\u7845 m h\u7843 i th\u7847 n n\u7893 i s\'f3ng, r\u7891 i ch\'e8o thuy\u7873 n \u273 \u7871 n b\u7901  hang \u273 \'e1 Ng\u432  Tinh, gi\u7843  c\'e1ch c\u7847 m m\u7897 t ng\u432 \u7901 i s\u7855 p n\'e9m v\'e0o cho n\'f3 \u259 n. Ng\u432  Tinh h\'e1 mi\u7879 ng \u273 \u7883 nh nu\u7889 t. Long Qu\'e2n c\u7847 m m\u7897 t kh\u7889 i s\u7855 t nung \u273 \u7887  n\'e9m v\'e0o mi\u7879 ng c\'e1. Ng\u432  Tinh ch\u7891 m l\'ean qu\u7851 y m\'ecnh qu\u7853 t v\'e0o thuy\u7873 n. Long Qu\'e2n c\u7855 t \u273 \u7913 t \u273 u\'f4i c\'e1, l\u7897 t da ph\u7911  l\'ean tr\'ean n\'fai nay ch\u7895  \u273 \'f3 g\u7885 i l\'e0\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/B%E1%BA%A1ch_Long_V%C4%A9"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 B\uc0\u7841 ch Long V\u297 }}, c\'f2n c\'e1i \uc0\u273 \u7847 u tr\'f4i ra ngo\'e0i b\u7875  bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh con ch\'f3. Long Qu\'e2n b\'e8n l\u7845 y \u273 \'e1 ng\u259 n b\u7875  r\u7891 i ch\'e9m n\'f3. N\'f3 bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh c\'e1i \u273 \u7847 u ch\'f3, nay g\u7885 i l\'e0\'a0
