\f1\b0 \cf2 Th\'e0nh\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Th%C4%83ng_Long"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 Th\uc0\u259 ng Long}}\'a0x\uc0\u432 a hi\u7879 u l\'e0\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Long_Bi%C3%AAn"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 Long Bi\'ean}}, h\uc0\u7891 i th\u432 \u7907 ng c\u7893  kh\'f4ng c\'f3 ng\u432 \u7901 i \u7903 . Vua Th\'e1i T\u7893 \'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nh%C3%A0_L%C3%BD"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 nh\'e0 L\'fd}}\'a0ch\'e8o thuy\uc0\u7873 n \u7903  b\u7871 n s\'f4ng Nh\u297  H\'e0, c\'f3 hai con r\u7891 ng d\u7851 n thuy\u7873 n \u273 i, cho n\'ean \u273 \u7863 t t\'ean l\'e0 Th\u259 ng Long r\u7891 i \u273 \'f3ng \u273 \'f4 \u7903  \u273 \u7845 y, ng\'e0y nay t\u7913 c l\'e0 th\'e0nh Kinh Hoa v\u7853 y. X\u432 a \u7903  ph\'eda t\'e2y th\'e0nh c\'f3 h\'f2n n\'fai \u273 \'e1 nh\u7887 , ph\'eda \u273 \'f4ng g\u7889 i l\'ean\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/S"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 s\'f4ng L\'f4 Giang}}. Trong hang, d\uc0\u432 \u7899 i ch\'e2n n\'fai, c\'f3 con c\'e1o tr\u7855 ng ch\'edn \u273 u\'f4i s\u7889 ng h\u417 n ng\'e0n n\u259 m, c\'f3 th\u7875  h\'f3a th\'e0nh y\'eau qu\'e1i, th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i ho\u7863 c th\'e0nh qu\u7927  \u273 i kh\u7855 p nh\'e2n gian. Th\u7901 i \u273 \'f3, d\u432 \u7899 i ch\'e2n\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/D%25C3%25A3y_n%25C3%25B"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 n\'fai T\uc0\u7843 n Vi\'ean}}, ng\uc0\u432 \u7901 i M\'e1n ch\'f4n g\u7895  k\u7871 t c\u7887  l\'e0m nh\'e0. Tr\'ean n\'fai c\'f3 v\u7883  th\u7847 n r\u7845 t linh thi\'eang, ng\u432 \u7901 i M\'e1n th\u432 \u7901 ng th\u7901  ph\u7909 ng. Th\u7847 n d\u7841 y ng\u432 \u7901 i M\'e1n tr\u7891 ng l\'faa, d\u7879 t v\u7843 i l\'e0m \'e1o tr\u7855 ng m\'e0 m\u7863 c cho n\'ean g\u7885 i l\'e0 B\u7841 ch Y Man (M\'e1n \'e1o tr\u7855 ng).\
Con c\'e1o ch\'edn \uc0\u273 u\'f4i bi\u7871 n th\'e0nh ng\u432 \u7901 i \'e1o tr\u7855 ng nh\u7853 p v\'e0o gi\u7919 a \u273 \'e1m d\'e2n M\'e1n c\'f9ng ca h\'e1t r\u7891 i d\u7909  d\u7895  trai g\'e1i tr\u7889 n v\'e0o trong hang n\'fai. Ng\u432 \u7901 i M\'e1n r\u7845 t kh\u7893  s\u7903 . Long Qu\'e2n b\'e8n ra l\u7879 nh cho l\u7909 c b\u7897  Th\u7911 y ph\u7911  d\'e2ng n\u432 \u7899 c l\'ean c\'f4ng ph\'e1 hang \u273 \'e1. C\'e1o ch\'edn \u273 u\'f4i b\u7887  ch\u7841 y, qu\'e2n Th\u7911 y ph\u7911  \u273 u\u7893 i theo, ph\'e1 hang b\u7855 t c\'e1o m\'e0 nu\u7889 t \u259 n. N\u417 i n\'e0y tr\u7903  th\'e0nh m\u7897 t c\'e1i v\u361 ng s\'e2u g\u7885 i l\'e0\'a0
\f4\i "\uc0\u273 \u7847 m x\'e1c c\'e1o"
